0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"How to get ISO 41001 certification in Dubai"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:45+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"Looking for ISO FMS 41001 certification in Dubai? Check out six essential steps to get ISO 41001 certification in Dubai and all over the UAE."}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How to get ISO 41001 certification in Dubai"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 41001 standard"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 41001:2018 is standard for facility management (FM) was released in April 2018 by International Standard Organization. It is designed to help organizations help establish, maintain and improve facility management compliance programs. ISO 41001 is vital for facility managers because it helps to reduce the possibility of human error and thus increases productivity."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"What is facility management?"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Facility management is the maintenance of the organization’s buildings and equipment. Facility management includes:"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Housekeeping"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Maintenance of plant and facility"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Security of organization."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Transportation"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Parking and visitor management"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How to get ISO 41001 certification in Dubai?"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"International standards are an essential strategic resource that can help your organization to meet its more pressing challenges. While it takes time, money and effort to obtain the ISO certification, it will allow your business to profit from enhanced processes and controls although providing to the organization with additional customer reputation. You will first need to establish and document your organization's processes before you can get ISO FMS 41001 certification and implementing the right procedures to ensure that you can maintain quality standards."}],["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms focus more on awareness, ISO training and ISO implementation of FMS standards to improve the industry's best practices and return on investment. Our easy and efficient consulting strategies ensure successful execution at your company. We simplify the process of ISO certification in Dubai and all over the UAE. We appoint a customer representative to direct you and your organization through the next steps after we have received your request. Here are the six essential steps to get ISO 41001 certification in Dubai."}],"$L2","$L3","$L4","$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9","$La","$Lb","$Lc","$Ld","$Le"]}],"$Lf"]}]}],["$L10"],"$L11"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
2:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Simple steps to get ISO 41001 certification in Dubai. 1) GAP analysis"}]
3:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"A survey for company requirements and the standard requirement is done to produce a detailed GAP analysis report."}]
4:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"2) Documentation"}]
5:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Based on the detailed study of all activities within an organization, documents are prepared, as required by ISO 41001 standards."}]
6:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"3) ISO Training"}]
7:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Provide awareness training to all employees within an organization."}]
8:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"4. Implementation"}]
9:["$","p","20",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Now is the right time to implement the ISO 41001 Facility Management (FM) system throughout the company. In this step, the required changes should be carried out an auditor visits the organization to make sure that effective changes are carried out based on the documentation."}]
a:["$","p","21",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"5) Internal Audit"}]
b:["$","p","22",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Employees will be trained on ways to conduct an internal audit to check readiness for ISO 41001 certification."}]
c:["$","p","23",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"6) ISO 41001 Certification"}]
d:["$","p","24",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"To obtain an FMS certification in Dubai, the auditor visits your company and completes the site audit. Perform the final audit and take appropriate actions on the defects and risks found to satisfy the certifying body. You will receive an ISO 41001 certification once you pass all the assessments. This ISO certification will be valid for 3 years."}]
e:["$","p","25",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Get your business ISO certification to improve the employee's health and safety and reduce the impact on the environment. Visit our website and submit queries with all your details to get your business ISO FMS 41001 certification in Dubai and rest of the UAE. One of our ISO certification experts will contact you as soon as possible to better understand your needs and provide the best solution available on the market."}]
